title: Pixel 3Xl top speaker make electric noise , that sounds like 'tick tick tick'
content:
Pixel 3Xl top speaker make electric noise , that sounds like 'tick tick tick', all time even in a lockscreen, when I reboot phone that sound loose for a second, but comes again. That's happen after December update, reseting of the phone doesn't helps me.
Update: found the main problem - USB connection, when I plug charging cable sound miss
category: Contacts, Calls, Voicemail, Google Pixel 3 XL
